<HEADLINE>
FT  01 MAY 91 / International Capital Markets: New M&amp;A chief at Credit
Lyonnais
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By DAVID LASCELLES, Banking Editor
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
CREDIT Lyonnais has appointed a new head of cross-border merger and
acquisition activity, writes David Lascelles, Banking Editor. He is Mr
Jean-Luc Biamonti.
Mr Biamonti was previously responsible for European development at
Wasserstein Perella, the US corporate finance house. Before that he worked
on international M&amp;A at First Boston, the Wall Street firm whose executives
founded Wasserstein Perella.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
London Page 28
