FT  01 MAY 91 / Oil R&amp;D project
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Department of Energy has announced a Pounds 12m research and development
programme on oilfield technology. The programme will be conducted in
conjunction with the Natural Environment Research Council, the
government-funded agency.
